President Obama announced his intent to nominate Heidi Biggs for the position of Member, Board of Directors of the Corporation for National and Community Service. Biggs currently serves as the Executive Director for the Community Foundation of the Klamath Basin. She has previously held various roles in public affairs and as an attorney. Biggs has also served on the Board of Directors for the Klamath-Lake Child Abuse Response & Evaluation Services. She holds a B.S. from Northwestern University and a J.D. from Willamette University.